snippet.title: NileRed Shorts
snippet.description: I'll be using this channel to combine all of the shorter NileRed videos that I've made on other platforms (Snapchat, Instagram, Tiktok, Twitter, etc), but I'll also make short videos that will be posted here before anywhere else!
